OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773828292
OL,3,CFrom regional powers to Brexit -
OL,4,CReeves signals long-term structural
OL,5,Cchange
OL,7,FThe Mais Lecture has a long history of
OL,8,Fchancellors setting out their economic
OL,9,Fphilosophy, and Reeves is making her
OL,10,Fposition pretty clear: the Treasury
OL,11,Fhaving full control of tax revenue is
OL,12,Fnot beneficial for the country.
OL,14,FToday, Reeves confirmed that regional
OL,15,Fmayors, figures like Andy Burnham in
OL,16,FGreater Manchester, will be handed
OL,17,Fcontrol of a share of national tax
OL,18,Frevenue. Treasury officials are
OL,19,Falready working on the road map we
OL,20,Fwere told about today.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
