FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773828292
OL,3,CFrom regional powers to Brexit -
OL,4,CReeves signals long-term structural
OL,5,Cchange
OL,7,FIt's significant because it will give
OL,8,Fmore power and influence to the
OL,9,Fregions, and, as I was once told, the
OL,10,FTreasury, in particular, has
OL,11,Fhistorically regarded fiscal
OL,12,Fdevolution with something close to
OL,13,Finstitutional suspicion.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773828292
OL,3,CFrom regional powers to Brexit -
OL,4,CReeves signals long-term structural
OL,5,Cchange
OL,7,FReeves is clearly ready and willing to
OL,8,Fpush through that resistance, and we
OL,9,Fare expecting details in the Autumn
OL,10,Fbudget.
OL,12,FOne of her other big statements was
OL,13,Fthat Brexit had caused "deep damage".
OL,15,FHer case was methodical - GDP impact
OL,16,Fof up to 8%, higher costs for
OL,17,Fbusinesses and a shrinking market for
OL,18,FUK exporters.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773828292
OL,3,CFrom regional powers to Brexit -
OL,4,CReeves signals long-term structural
OL,5,Cchange
OL,7,FThese are not new numbers, but having
OL,8,Fthe chancellor read them from a
OL,9,Flectern in the City of London, in a
OL,10,Froom full of senior figures from
OL,11,Fwithin the finance capital of the
OL,12,Fcountry, is a different thing entirely.
OL,14,FThe danger for Labour is obvious. It
OL,15,Fis one thing to quietly pursue a post-
OL,16,FBrexit reset through technical
OL,17,Fagreements; it is another to hand the
OL,18,Fopposition an attack line as clean as
OL,19,Fthis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
