FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773828292
OL,3,CFrom regional powers to Brexit -
OL,4,CReeves signals long-term structural
OL,5,Cchange
OL,7,FOpposition parties will inevitably
OL,8,Faccuse Reeves and the government of
OL,9,Fwanting to "row back on Brexit" -
OL,10,Fparticularly if they choose to opt for
OL,11,Fa closer relationship.
OL,13,FWhat exactly that looks like is
OL,14,Funclear - but it is expected to be
OL,15,Flooked at as part of the annual
OL,16,Fprocess of bilateral talks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
