FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773828292
OL,3,CFrom regional powers to Brexit -
OL,4,CReeves signals long-term structural
OL,5,Cchange
OL,7,FThe two announcements do, in their
OL,8,Fdifferent ways, highlight the same
OL,9,Fthing: the government believes longer-
OL,10,Fterm structural change is needed. Both
OL,11,Fwill take time, but both could
OL,12,Fcertainly have a profound impact if
OL,13,Fdone in the way they've been billed.
OL,15,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,16,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,17,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,18,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
